      "title": "Claude Fable Guide for Stock Analysis",
      "link": "https://www.ai-supremacy.com/p/claude-fable-guide-for-stock-analysis-anthropic-mythos-july-2026",
      "published": "2026-07-08",
      "content": "\n\n👋 大家好，我是迈克。每周我都会分享科技、商业、社会与未来交汇处的AI相关文章。我也会尽力分享来自世界各地作家的作品。如果你想要支持这个频道或获得我作品的完整访问权限，请点击这里。阅读存档 | 查看Substack笔记 | 加入我们的社区聊天 | 访问首页。我做这件事已经五年了，AI仍然是一个值得关注的话题。\n\n今天的客座作家是来自马来西亚的Weng Honn Kan。这是我们“用Claude进行投资”系列文章的第二篇，你可以在这里阅读第一篇。\n\nClaude的Fable 5模型有着相当传奇的故事。赶紧将它用于投资目的，因为付费Claude用户只有四天时间使用Fable，之后它将在7月12日转换为按token计费模式。代理型AI即将真正改变我们的投资方式和选股方法。\n\n撰写出版物《如何用AI投资》。\n发现最佳的AI股票分析工具和投资策略。\nWeng Lab：构建、测试和审查AI投资工具，了解更多关于。\n如何使用Claude进行投资：四级系统（AI角落）\n用Claude找出任何市场趋势的赢家（与AI复合）\n用Claude构建你自己的股票分析师\n\n让我们进入今天的指南：\n\n我如何设置Claude Fable 5进行股票研究，以及我的三项技能中哪些真正需要它。\n\n大约两周半的时间里，你能合法使用的最强大AI模型……就这么消失了。\n\n2026年6月12日，美国商务部命令Anthropic暂停Claude Fable 5（及其封闭版本Mythos 5）。触发点是亚马逊研究人员发现的一次越狱攻击——一个能让模型标记软件漏洞并在某些情况下写出如何被滥用的代码的提示。由于该命令适用于任何外国公民，而Anthropic无法实时检查每个用户的护照，他们为所有人按下了暂停键。\n\n然后，6月30日，控制措施被解除。Fable 5在7月1日重新上线，覆盖Claude.ai、Claude Code和Cowork。\n\n我不会告诉你它“被禁用是因为太强大，可能会震惊世界”。那是网络上的说法。真正对你作为投资者有用的版本是：一个政府认为足够严重以至于动用紧急出口管制的模型——这是Anthropic发布给公众的有史以来最强大的模型——现在就在你已经使用的同一个应用中。这才是值得关注的重点。\n\n所以这周是一篇实践性文章。我将向你展示我如何精确地设置Fable进行股票研究，它真正擅长什么，以及——这是大多数人都搞错的部分——我的三项技能中哪些真正需要它，哪些浪费它会很愚蠢。\n\n让我们开始吧。\n\nClaude Fable 5到底是什么（以及它有何不同）\nFable真正最擅长的——以及它显得大材小用的场景\n框架：Fable决策网格\n我如何用Claude Fable设置我的投资AI系统。\n如何为你的股票研究设置Fable——分步骤指南\n用正确的技能做正确的工作。\n\n让我们深入了解……\n阅读更多",
      "summary": "<div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/subscribe\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><source type=\"image/webp\" /><img alt=\"Anthropic releases Claude Fable 5, its most powerful public AI model\" class=\"sizing-normal\" height=\"971\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!XtH8!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc57b8cb1-619b-42c8-97ee-1e8de9cd04c8_1920x1280.jpeg\" title=\"Anthropic releases Claude Fable 5, its most powerful public AI model\" width=\"1456\" /><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\" fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>&#128075; <em>Hey there, I&#8217;m Mike. Each week I share AI articles at the intersection of tech, business, society and the future. I also try to share the work of writers from all around the world. If you want to support the channel or gain full-access to my work, go <a href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/subscribe\">here</a>. Read <a href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/archive\">Archives</a> | See Substack <a href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/notes\">Notes</a> | Visit our community <a href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/chat\">Chat </a>| Visit <a href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/\">Homepage</a>. I&#8217;ve been doing this for five years and AI is still a worthwhile topic. </em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/subscribe\"><span>Get Full Access</span></a></p><div><hr /></div><p>Our guest writer today is <strong><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/iamwenghonn/\">Weng Honn Kan</a>, from Malaysia. </strong>This is the second article in our <strong>Claude for Investing series</strong>, you can read the first article by <span class=\"mention-wrap\"></span> <a href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/p/how-to-use-claude-ai-for-investing-equities-research\">here</a>. </p><p class=\"button-wrapper\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/p/how-to-use-claude-ai-for-investing-equities-research\"><span>Claude AI for Equity Research</span></a></p><p>Claude&#8217;s <a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/2026/jun/11/fable-is-relentlessly-proactive/\">Fable 5</a> model has <a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/news/redeploying-fable-5\">quite the story</a>. Hurry to use it for Investing purposes as Paid Claude users <strong>get just four more days</strong> with<a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/15424964-claude-fable-5-promotional-access\"> Fable before it shifts</a> to pay-per-token pricing on July 12th. Agentic AI is about to really change how we do investing and pick stocks. </p><p><span class=\"mention-wrap\"></span> writes the publication <a href=\"https://thewenglab.substack.com/\">How to Invest with AI</a>. </p><h3>How to Invest with AI </h3><p>Discover the best AI stock analysis tools and investing strategies. </p><div class=\"embedded-publication-wrap\"><div class=\"embedded-publication show-subscribe\"><a class=\"embedded-publication-link-part\" href=\"https://thewenglab.substack.com?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_campaign=publication_embed&amp;utm_medium=web\"><img class=\"embedded-publication-logo\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!nO1P!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5f5338b-1830-4a6f-8363-ebdf8a081d29_1080x1080.png\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" width=\"56\" /><span class=\"embedded-publication-name\">How to Invest with AI</span><div class=\"embedded-publication-hero-text\">Discover the best AI stock analysis tools and investing strategies. We test every AI tool with real money to show you what works and what doesn't , so you can build an AI investment strategy that actually pays off.</div><div class=\"embedded-publication-author-name\">By Weng Honn</div></a><form action=\"https://thewenglab.substack.com/subscribe?\" class=\"embedded-publication-subscribe\" method=\"GET\"><input name=\"source\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"publication-embed\" /><input name=\"autoSubmit\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"true\" /><input class=\"email-input\" name=\"email\" type=\"email\" /><input class=\"button primary\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe\" /></form></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>Weng Lab</strong>: Building, Testing, and Reviewing AI Investing Tools, <a href=\"https://thewenglab.substack.com/about\">Learn more About</a>. </p></li></ul><h3>Related Articles and Resources </h3><ul><li><p>How to use Claude for Investing: <a href=\"https://www.the-ai-corner.com/p/claude-for-investing-4-level-system\">the 4-Level System</a> (AI Corner) </p></li><li><p>Find the winners of <a href=\"https://news.aiinvestinghq.com/p/find-the-winners-of-any-market-trend\">any market trend with claude</a> (Compound with AI) </p></li><li><p>Build your own <a href=\"https://news.aiinvestinghq.com/p/build-your-own-stock-analyst-with\">stock analyst with Claude</a></p></li></ul><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!2I6F!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcc448ac3-a8fa-4778-848f-4f29ef4dc797_1400x900.png\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><source type=\"image/webp\" /><img alt=\"\" class=\"sizing-normal\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!2I6F!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcc448ac3-a8fa-4778-848f-4f29ef4dc797_1400x900.png\" width=\"1400\" /><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\" fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">Compound with AI. </figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"button-wrapper\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://news.aiinvestinghq.com/\"><span>Read Compound with AI</span></a></p><p>Let&#8217;s get into today&#8217;s guide: </p><h2>Claude Fable Guide for Stock Analysis</h2><h4><span>The Complete Guide to Using AI to Spot Undervalued AI Stocks</span></h4><p><span>How I set up Claude Fable 5 for stock research , and which of my 3 skills actually need it .</span></p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Lszh!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9d94a602-e02a-4827-b258-a8d4629fc972_1456x830.jpeg\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><source type=\"image/webp\" /><img alt=\"\" class=\"sizing-normal\" height=\"830\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Lszh!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9d94a602-e02a-4827-b258-a8d4629fc972_1456x830.jpeg\" width=\"1456\" /><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\" fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><h4><strong><span>The model they tried to ban is back. Here&#8217;s how I point it at stocks.</span></strong></h4><p><span>For about two and a half weeks, the most capable AI model you could legally touch simply&#8230; vanished.</span></p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bm5d!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8f2d5d1-209c-41ad-8678-ed2609e5251c_1456x830.jpeg\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><source type=\"image/webp\" /><img alt=\"\" class=\"sizing-normal\" height=\"830\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bm5d!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8f2d5d1-209c-41ad-8678-ed2609e5251c_1456x830.jpeg\" width=\"1456\" /><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\" fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><span>On </span><strong><span>June 12, 2026</span></strong><span>, the U.S. Commerce Department ordered Anthropic to suspend Claude Fable 5 (and its locked-down sibling, Mythos 5). The trigger was a jailbreak that Amazon&#8217;s researchers found , a prompt that got the model to flag software flaws and, in one case, write code showing how one could be abused. Because the order applied to any foreign national and Anthropic couldn&#8217;t check every user&#8217;s passport in real time, they pulled the plug for </span><em><span>everyone</span></em><span>.</span></p><p><span>Then, on </span><strong><span>June 30</span></strong><span>, the controls were lifted. Fable 5 came back online on </span><strong><span>July 1</span></strong><span> across Claude.ai, Claude Code, and Cowork.</span></p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!GrRS!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63cfa3ea-afc2-495d-bc18-6d86eb1cd592_1456x830.jpeg\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><source type=\"image/webp\" /><img alt=\"\" class=\"sizing-normal\" height=\"830\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!GrRS!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63cfa3ea-afc2-495d-bc18-6d86eb1cd592_1456x830.jpeg\" width=\"1456\" /><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\" fill=\"none\" height=\"20\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><span>I&#8217;m not going to tell you it was &#8220;taken out because it&#8217;s too powerful and might shock the world.&#8221; That&#8217;s the internet&#8217;s version. The real version is more useful to you as an investor: the single most capable model Anthropic has ever released to the public was considered </span><em><span>serious enough</span></em><span> that a government reached for emergency export controls &#8212; and it&#8217;s now sitting in the same app you already use. That&#8217;s the part worth paying attention to.</span></p><p><span>So this week is a hands-on one. I&#8217;ll show you exactly how I set Fable up for stock research, what it&#8217;s genuinely better at, and &#8212; the part most people get wrong &#8212; which of my three skills actually </span><em><span>need</span></em><span> it, and which ones you&#8217;d be silly to waste it on.</span></p><p><span>Let&#8217;s get into it.</span></p><h2><strong><span>In this sharing you will get:</span></strong></h2><ol><li><p><span>What Claude Fable 5 actually is (and why it&#8217;s different)</span></p></li><li><p><span>What Fable is genuinely best for &#8212; and what it&#8217;s overkill for</span></p></li><li><p><span>The framework: the Fable Decision Grid</span></p></li><li><p><span>How I set up my investment AI system using Claude Fable .</span></p></li><li><p><span>How to set up Fable for your stock research &#8212; step by step</span></p></li><li><p><span>Get the right skills to do the right job.</span></p></li></ol><p><span>Let&#8217;s dive in&#8230;</span></p>\n      <p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.ai-supremacy.com/p/claude-fable-guide-for-stock-analysis-anthropic-mythos-july-2026\">\n              Read more\n          </a>\n      </p>",
